Steve Bruce, meanwhile, appears to have ruled himself out of the running for the position at St James’ Park, although were an approach forthcoming that stance could well change.

Derby boss Steve McClaren is thought to be another name the United hierarchy are considering.

Any appointment, however, is not expected until next week at the earliest.

